---
title: Turkey and Veggie Chow Mein with Veggie Medley
description: Bust out your chopsticks for this deliciously sweet, spicy and umami chow mein dish! Stir-fried peppers and cabbage get a fragrant boost from a Moo Shu Spices Blend ginger and fresh green onions, but it's the soy-sweet chili sauce that will really make your taste buds sing!
